cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.DS 

The paper discusses active learning algorithms for binary classification with a reject option. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and data structures (cs.DS) as it involves developing algorithms to efficiently reduce the number of labeled examples required for classification tasks.
